{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ca0f43156c","title":"李富春接见国家计委同志谈斗争薄一波","origin":"中国人民大学、南开大学合办《新人大 新南开》1967年9月15日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33b3995d11","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"ca0f43156c"}],"tags":[{"id":"25e2abfb25","name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9c4175f9ee","name":"李富春"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"99a7e9cfdf","type":"title","text":"李富春接见国家计委同志谈斗争薄一波","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"cba083eedb","type":"authors","text":"李富春","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"52102bb5aa","type":"paragraph","text":"摘要：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"cc283d4284","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争薄一波，要挖他的历史根子，要挖痛。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"a612133309","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、挖（他）是刘少奇包庇下来的叛徒（下边未听清）。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"28e22aa6a7","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、投奔阎锡山，把大叛徒宋劭文、牛佩琮、戎子和等搞到山西去。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"8a78aed974","type":"paragraph","text":"第三、抗战时期搞“牺盟会”、“决死队”。“牺盟会”负责人是戎子和（下一个未听清）。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"},{"id":"a577c5140b","type":"paragraph","text":"第四、薄一波的一套手法是阎锡山那里来的，以后和刘少奇、刘澜涛、安子文等大叛徒勾结起来，到处伸手。你搞他的具体问题，他可以躲闪。你搞他的历史问题，他就没有办法。自首叛变61个人，是刘少奇批的，没有报告主席，没有报告中央，是同张闻天勾结起来搞的，主席不知道。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c"}],"page":{"id":"1c4b0a8b93","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ca0f43156c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}